KangKang2024KDRegression	Article	true	Kang, Myeonginn and Kang, Seokho	2024	Knowledge Distillation with Insufficient Training Data for Regression	Engineering Applications of Artificial Intelligence		132		108001	10.1016/j.engappai.2024.108001					https://doi.org/10.1016/j.engappai.2024.108001	manual_required		No clearly legal open PDF/HTML download was found automatically; use the DOI/URL manually or through institutional access if needed.	thesis.tex:646	thesis_zh.tex:462	Recent work on knowledge distillation for regression under data scarcity has shown that teacher-soft targets can substantially reduce student prediction error precisely in regimes where direct labels are missing \cite{KangKang2024KDRegression} --- which is the regime this thesis lands in by construction.	ŤŅĎśúüŚÖ≥šļéŚõěŚĹíŤíłť¶ŹšłéšłćŚģĆśēīÁõĎÁĚ£ÁöĄÁ†ĒÁ©∂šĻüŤ°®śėéÔľĆśēôŚłąŤĹĮÁõģś†áŚŹĮšĽ•Śú®Áõīśé•ś†áÁ≠ĺÁľļŚ§ĪśąĖšłćŚŹĮťĚ†ŚĆļŚüüśėĺŤĎóťôćšĹéŚ≠¶ÁĒüŤĮĮŚ∑ģ \cite{HintonVinyalsDean2015,TarvainenValpola2017,KangKang2024KDRegression}„Äā	Supports knowledge distillation specifically in regression with insufficient training data.	ÁĒ®šļéśĒĮśíĎŤģ≠ÁĽÉśēįśćģšłćŤ∂≥śó∂Śú®ŚõěŚĹíšĽĽŚä°šł≠ťááÁĒ®Áü•ŤĮÜŤíłť¶Ź„Äā	Checked direct URL, arXiv when applicable, and OpenAlex OA metadata.
Baumgarten2006MixFormation	Book	true	Baumgarten, Carsten	2006	Mixture Formation in Internal Combustion Engines		Springer				10.1007/3-540-30836-9					https://doi.org/10.1007/3-540-30836-9	manual_required		No clearly legal open PDF/HTML download was found automatically; use the DOI/URL manually or through institutional access if needed.	thesis.tex:108 || thesis.tex:682 || thesis.tex:685	thesis_zh.tex:115 || thesis_zh.tex:495 || thesis_zh.tex:497	Diesel-spray research has also long used empirical penetration correlations and phenomenological models to describe spray development rapidly; in this context, comparing penetration with wall distance provides a natural first-order geometric criterion for impingement screening \cite{HiroyasuArai1990,NaberSiebers1996,Baumgarten2006MixFormation}. || The simplest screening rule used in engineering practice has barely changed in two decades: compare the liquid-phase spray-tip penetration $S_\mathrm{tip}(t)$ against the nozzle-to-wall distance $L_\mathrm{wall}$, and flag impingement once $S_\mathrm{tip}(t) \geq L_\mathrm{wall}$ \cite{Baumgarten2006MixFormation}. || Baumgarten's reference treatment of mixture formation in internal combustion engines codifies this practice, naming penetration correlations as the baseline trajectory descriptor and the penetration-to-wall-distance comparison as the default first-order impingement criterion \cite{Baumgarten2006MixFormation}.	śüīś≤ĻŚĖ∑ťõĺÁ†ĒÁ©∂šĻüťēŅśúüšĹŅÁĒ®ÁĽŹť™ĆÁ©Ņś∑ĪŚÖ≥ŤĀĒŚľŹŚíĆÁéįŤĪ°Ś≠¶ś®°ŚěčŚŅęťÄüśŹŹŤŅįŚĖ∑ťõĺŚŹĎŚĪēÔľĆ ŚÖ∂šł≠Á©Ņś∑ĪšłéŚ£ĀŤ∑ĚÁöĄśĮĒŤĺÉśěĄśąźšļÜšłÄťė∂śíěŚ£ĀÁ≠õśü•ÁöĄŤá™ÁĄ∂Śá†šĹēŚą§śćģ \cite{HiroyasuArai1990,NaberSiebers1996,Baumgarten2006MixFormation}„Äā || Ś∑•Á®čšłäśúÄÁõīśé•ÁöĄÁ≠õśü•ŤßĄŚąôÁõłŚĮĻśėéÁ°ģÔľö śĮĒŤĺÉś∂≤ÁõłŚįĖÁęĮÁ©Ņś∑Ī $S_\mathrm{tip}(t)$ šłéŚĖ∑ŚėīŚąįŚ£ĀťĚĘÁöĄŤ∑ĚÁ¶Ľ $L_\mathrm{wall}$ÔľĆŚĹď \(S_\mathrm{tip}(t) \geq L_\mathrm{wall}\) śó∂ś†áŤģįšłļśíěŚ£Ā \cite{Baumgarten2006MixFormation}„Äā || Baumgarten ŚÖ≥šļéŚÜÖÁáÉśúļś∑∑ŚźąśįĒŚĹĘśąźÁöĄÁ≥ĽÁĽüŤģļŤŅįšł≠ÔľĆšĻüśääÁ©Ņś∑ĪŚÖ≥ŤĀĒŚľŹŤßÜšłļÁģÄŚĆĖŚĖ∑ťõĺŤĹ®ŤŅĻÁöĄŚüļÁļŅŚ∑•ŚÖ∑ÔľĆŚĻ∂śääÁ©Ņś∑ĪšłéŚ£ĀŤ∑ĚśĮĒŤĺÉšĹúšłļšłÄťė∂śíěŚ£ĀŚą§śćģ \cite{Baumgarten2006MixFormation}„Äā	Supports the first-level wall-impingement criterion that compares spray-tip penetration with wall distance.	ÁĒ®šļéśĒĮśíĎŚįÜŚĖ∑ťõĺŚįĖÁęĮÁ©Ņś∑ĪšłéŚ£ĀŤ∑ĚśĮĒŤĺÉšĹúšłļšłÄÁļßśíěŚ£ĀÁ≠õśü•ŚáÜŚąô„Äā	Checked direct URL, arXiv when applicable, and OpenAlex OA metadata.
MorieiraMotaPanao2010	Article	true	Moreira, A. L. N. and Moita, A. S. and Panao, M. R.	2010	Advances and Challenges in Explaining Fuel Spray Impingement: How Much of Single Droplet Impact Research Is Useful?	Progress in Energy and Combustion Science		36	5	554-580	10.1016/j.pecs.2010.01.002					https://doi.org/10.1016/j.pecs.2010.01.002	manual_required		No clearly legal open PDF/HTML download was found automatically; use the DOI/URL manually or through institutional access if needed.	thesis.tex:95 || thesis.tex:668 || thesis.tex:673 || thesis.tex:1517	thesis_zh.tex:105 || thesis_zh.tex:473 || thesis_zh.tex:477 || thesis_zh.tex:1332	If its liquid envelope reaches the piston bowl or cylinder wall before a useful ignition kernel forms, wall wetting, lubricant dilution, degraded local mixture preparation, and increased unburned-hydrocarbon emissions may follow \cite{peraza2022swi,ahmad2025fueldilution,MorieiraMotaPanao2010}. || When liquid fuel reaches the piston bowl or cylinder wall before evaporation or ignition has had time to consume it, a fuel film deposits on the surface, and the downstream consequences --- wall wetting, locally deteriorated mixing, elevated unburned-hydrocarbon emissions, and lubricant dilution --- are well documented across both passenger-car and heavy-duty contexts \cite{peraza2022swi,ahmad2025fueldilution,MorieiraMotaPanao2010}. || } are explicit in their review that single-droplet impact research has accumulated a sizable knowledge base, but extrapolating it directly to continuous spray impingement is a stretch: a spray plume behaves collectively, and that collective behavior is shaped by neighbour-droplet interactions, residual wall film, and secondary atomization phenomena that simply do not appear in isolated droplet experiments \cite{MorieiraMotaPanao2010}. || The regime of primary concern is direct liquid-wall contact and persistent wall-film formation \cite{MorieiraMotaPanao2010,liu2024marine_impingement,peraza2022swi,ahmad2025fueldilution}.	Ťč•ś∂≤ÁõłŚĆÖÁĽúŚú®ŚĹĘśąźśúČśēąÁāĻÁĀęś†łšĻčŚČćŚ∑≤Ťß¶ŚŹäśīĽŚ°ěť°∂śąĖÁľłŚ£ĀÔľĆ ŚąôŚŹĮŤÉĹŚĮľŤáīŚ£ĀťĚĘś∂¶śĻŅ„ÄĀś∂¶śĽĎś≤ĻÁ®Äťáä„ÄĀŚĪÄťÉ®ś∑∑ŚźąśĀ∂ŚĆĖšĽ•ŚŹäśú™ÁáÉÁĘ≥śįĘśéíśĒĺŚćáťęėÁ≠ČšłćŚą©Śźéśěú \cite{peraza2022swi,ahmad2025fueldilution,MorieiraMotaPanao2010}„Äā || Ťč•ś∂≤śÄĀÁáÉśĖôŚú®ŤíłŚŹĎśąĖÁāĻÁĀęšĻčŚČćŚąįŤĺĺśīĽŚ°ěť°∂śąĖÁľłŚ£ĀÔľĆŚ£ĀťĚĘšłäŚŹĮŤÉĹŚĹĘśąźÁáÉś≤Ļś∂≤ŤÜúÔľĆŚĻ∂ťÄ†śąźŚ£ĀťĚĘś∂¶śĻŅ„ÄĀŚĪÄťÉ®ś∑∑ŚźąśĀ∂ŚĆĖ„ÄĀśú™ÁáÉÁĘ≥śįĘśéíśĒĺŚćáťęėšĽ•ŚŹäśúļś≤ĻÁ®Äťáä \cite{peraza2022swi,ahmad2025fueldilution,MorieiraMotaPanao2010}„Äā || Moreira Á≠ČŚú®ÁĽľŤŅįšł≠śĆáŚáļÔľĆŚćēś∂≤śĽīśíěŚáĽÁ†ĒÁ©∂Á°ģŚģěÁßĮÁīĮšļÜŚ§ßťáŹŚüļÁ°ÄÁü•ŤĮÜÔľĆ šĹÜŚįÜŚÖ∂Áõīśé•Ś§Ėśé®Ťá≥ŤŅěÁĽ≠ŚĖ∑ťõĺśíěŚ£ĀŚĻ∂šłćÁ®≥Ś¶•ÔľĆŚõ†šłļŚĖ∑ťõĺ plume ÁöĄťõÜšĹďŤ°ĆšłļŤŅėŚŹóŚąįťāĽŤŅĎś∂≤śĽīÁõłšļíšĹúÁĒ®„ÄĀśģčšĹôŚ£ĀŤÜúŚíĆšļĆś¨°ťõĺŚĆĖÁ≠ČŚõ†Áī†ŤįÉŚą∂ \cite{MorieiraMotaPanao2010}„Äā || Áúüś≠£ťúÄŤ¶ĀšľėŚÖąŚÖ≥ś≥®ÁöĄśėĮÁõīśé•ÁöĄś∂≤śĽīśíěŚ£ĀŚíĆśĆĀÁĽ≠Ś£ĀŤÜúŚĹĘśąź \cite{MorieiraMotaPanao2010,liu2024marine_impingement,peraza2022swi,ahmad2025fueldilution}„Äā	Supports the broader spray-impingement physics context and the difficulty of scaling droplet-impact knowledge to full sprays.	ÁĒ®šļéśĒĮśíĎŚĖ∑ťõĺśíěŚ£ĀÁČ©ÁźÜŤÉĆśôĮÔľĆšĽ•ŚŹäšĽéŚćēś∂≤śĽīÁĘįŚ£Āśé®ŚĻŅŚąįśēīšĹďŚĖ∑ťõĺÁöĄŚõįťöĺ„Äā	Checked direct URL, arXiv when applicable, and OpenAlex OA metadata.
